GoldenEye::
She dives and manuevers around GodFather. Is hit by a few shots, but 
returns fire iwth her optic lazars, firing 15 blasts at him.

::KitKat::
She wiggled and tried to get Destructor to let her go. but his grip 
was to strong. She got hit and howled out in pain from the missles.
Her sides were now leaking heavily.
